The first confirmed COVID-19 case can be traced back to 1 December 2019 in Wuhan; an unconfirmed report indicates the earliest cases on 17 November.
Dr. Zhang Jixian observed a cluster of pneumonia cases with unknown causes on December 26; his hospital reported the observation to Jianghan CDC on December 27.
